USES PORT;

VAR
   RS232Base [ORIGIN 16#0040:16#0000] : ARRAY [1..4] OF WORD;

   PROCEDURE RaiseDTRandRTS(PortNo : INTEGER);
   !旼컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴커
